page.title: 14ALL ABOUT FOOD I LIKE
page.content: Fish and chips is a nice food. You can get it in a fish and chip shop.You can get savaloy and chips, cod and chips, pie and chips and battered sausage, coka cola and other drinks.Sometimes you can go to a chinese restaurant to eat. You can get wun-tun soup, su-mai, char-soo, beet in oyster sauce, sweet and sour pork, crispy duck, rice. In English restaurants you can get fish and chips, scampi and other things. You can also get crisps, chocolate, ice cream and cakes. For my dinner I have rice and other things. On Sunday we have roast beef or lamb with potatoes and corn. Sometimes my dad goes to Chinatown and buys su-mai,char-soo, soy duck and rice roll. I like Chinese food. I hate English food. My mother is Chinese and my father is British. TRAFALGAR SCHOOL
